caption: The image is a Ramadhan Kareem greeting card. The text on the card reads "May this Ramadan bring you peace, harmony, and joy. I pray to Almighty Allah to protect and bless you. Ramadan Kareem!" The card is blue and features a crescent moon and stars. The website www.reallygreatsite.com is also displayed on the card.
original_title: Blue & Illustrated Realism Ramadan Greeting Socmed Story
texts: May this Ramadan bring you peace, harmony, and joy. I pray to Almighty Allah to protect and bless you. Ramadan Kareem!
